Description:
Great Size with 2 bedrooms & 2 bathrooms and Car park
Situated in the stylish Mosaic apartment complex, this large ground floor apartment makes a great place to call home or a good investment.
Currently leased on the NRAS scheme which offers great tax incentives or vacant possession available. Features an open plan design with large sun filled lounge, sizeable kitchen with gas cooktop and plenty of bench and cupboard space, 2 spacious bedrooms, both with BIRs, the convenience of 2 bathrooms and 2 toilets & private fenced & gated front courtyard.

With a bus stop and caf/restaurant meters from your front door, Dandenong Train Station and CBD a short stroll away & easy access to main arterials this is the place to be! Great value here, inspect today!

Additional Features : Gas ducted heating, Air conditioning, Single Garage plus workshop, extensive driveway with secure gates (ideal for people with trailers).

Appealing to investors and first home buyers alike, this 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home with impressive frontage is superbly located just a 10 minute walk from Yarraman station.
The home sits on a quiet street and combines classic charm with modern amenities. It has timber floorboards, ducted heating and built-in robes in each of the bedrooms.
The open-plan living room has a functional fireplace and is perfect for relaxing in, with a glass sliding door that opens up onto the front porch and generously proportioned front yard - making it great for entertaining.
With plenty of street parking for guests and a single-car garage accessible from the rear courtyard, the home is just 1 of 2 on the block, so there are no body corporate or strata fees.
This home needs to be seen to be truly appreciated, so get in touch and lock in an inspection today.

NEAR NEW ELEGANCE IN SUPERB LOCALE!
Ray White is proud to present luxury living in the heart of Dandenong. This one year old family residence is bound to charm even the fussiest of First Home Buyers, Upsizes and Investors. Quality built, street facing and situated in a highly desirable pocket of Dandenong, this home provides the ideal lifestyle you have been searching for!
This contemporary haven offers a spacious open plan lounge, kitchen and dining area on the ground floor. The lovely kitchen features stone benchtops, gas cooking, stainless steel appliances and ample cupboard space, The private low maintenance courtyard is perfect for outdoor enjoyment, the powder and laundry make up the rest of the ground floor.
The Master bedroom is carefully tucked away on the upper floor with Mirrored BIR and and full ensuite. Also upstairs are 2 good sized bedrooms with BIRs and luxurious bathroom with floor to ceiling tiles.
Features of this home include: Second kitchen in the garage with gas cooking and ample cupboard space, single remote garage, three split system air-conditioning/heating, garden shed and much more!
Located within a stone's throw away from Dandenong South Primary School, Dandenong Station, Dandenong CBD, Dandenong Bypass/Eastlink, public transport and recreational facilities. This home is all but ready for you to make it your own.
Do not miss out on this excellent opportunity!

Description:
5 Year Old Porter Davis Home in Meridian Estate
A truly unique opportunity presents itself to you right here with this almost new home in the highly sought after Meridian Estate. Only 5 years old, the quality built Porter Davis home is not only visually appealing but offers an array of features which will suit all modern family requirements. As you step inside the grand double door entry, one of the first things that you will appreciate is the openness that this home offers. Wide corridors and an expansive living zone which incorporates open planned kitchen, dining and family area at the rear of the home are ideal for entertainment, whilst the enclosed lounge/theatre room is perfect for snuggling up with your family after work and watching your favourite TV shows. Boasting 4 bedrooms including master suite with full en suite with double vanities and rainfall showerhead as well as impressive walk in robe, central family bathroom with shower niche and elegant, thin feature tiling, stunning two-pac finish kitchen with dual 600mm side by side ovens, 900mm gas cook top and canopy rangehood, dishwasher, glass splashbacks and all cesar stone benchtops include waterfall finish which incorporates breakfast bar and adjoining walk in pantry. Externally the home features a magnificent deck area with inbuilt seating and accessible from both lounge and family areas via double sliding doors, making it perfect for hosting summer barbeques or simply basking in the hot sun. Incorporating central gas ducted heating, evaporative cooling, porcelain tiles through main living areas and kitchen, quality carpets in bedrooms and lounge room, downlights in all living zones and feature drop down lighting in kitchen area, security alarm system as well as front door video surveillance and plantation shutters, this home truly has it all. With parks and walking tracks just around the corner and a truly quiet street which is perfect for your kids to get outside and play in, this property is one of the best family homes that you will find in Dandenong. Arrange to inspect before it is too late!

Keep the Front, Build at the Back or Demolish & Build 3 (STCA)
Positioned in one of central Dandenongs best locations, this property which sits on a lot size of 753 sqm (approximately) makes an outstanding development prospect. With walking access to all amenities including Dandenong Hospital, High School, Market and Plaza as well as public transport services and Dandenongs CBD, the property is perfectly positioned for future capital growth and high resale of newly built dwellings on the land. The existing solid brick home provides enormous character and potential and with a small investment can be updated to a modern masterpiece with possibility to retain and build an additional dwelling in the backyard (STCA). Alternatively you can bring your bulldozer and start from scratch with potential to redevelop the entire block with 3 brand new townhouses/units (STCA). Comprising 2 bedrooms, formal lounge area or potentially 3rd bedroom, open kitchen and dining area, central family bathroom and separate toilet and beautifully light filled family room/sunroom which overlooks the backyard. With existing tenant currently paying $340 per week this property makes a perfect investment. Arrange to inspect before it is too late!

Description:
GOLDEN OPPORTUNITY NOT TO BE MISSED!
Enviably situated in the coveted Metro Village Estate, the immediate appeal of this modern residence is more than matched by the spacious interiors that brilliantly showcase the home's allure with a contemporary floor plan. Looked after as a loving family home deserves to be, this immaculate haven has an inviting Open Plan Living with ample kitchen cabinets and pantries, a separate dining area and spacious second living area.
The Master bedroom is carefully tucked away on the upper floor with a extra-large Walk in Robe and an Ensuite with his and hers sinks to ensure maximum privacy. Upper floor also presents 3 good sized bedrooms with BIRs, separate toilet and main bathroom featuring a bathtub.
A remote controlled double garage and a private courtyard is ideal for families. A delightful surprise package, it also includes ducted heating throughout the home, split system and much more!.
Desirably situated opposite the Dandenong Station, within a short walking distance to the retail precinct like Dandenong Plaza and Market, local businesses, pre schools, primary schools, high schools and an abundance of multicultural eateries. Commuting to the city is made easy with Eastlink and Princes Highway close by and Public Transport is within reach.
For further information on how you can make all these yours, please come down to the Open Home or feel free to contact us to take you through privately
Call Ben Jusufi or Burak Gul today for further information!
